<materialsCitation id="3B041B3AFFDFFFEBFB485B9A5E98FB97" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3804303386" pageId="50" pageNumber="602">“Fazenda do Bené, 4 km SE Passa Vinte, Minas Gerais, Brazil, 22°14’S 44°12°’W, 680 m.”</materialsCitation>
